HTML = '''<h1>Integrated Quality, Safety, and Environmental (QSE) Policy</h1>
<p><strong>[Company Name]</strong> is committed to excellence across every project delivery discipline. We integrate quality, safety, and environmental stewardship through our digital QSE Management System to meet contractual, statutory, and community expectations.</p>
<p>This policy is controlled through the QSE portal at <code>/qse/corp-policy-roles</code> and is indexed within the Master Document &amp; Records Register (QSE-7.5-REG-01). The published version links to supporting procedures, registers, and dashboards in accordance with the knowledge graph.</p>
<h2>Our Commitment</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Client Value:</strong> Deliver projects that satisfy requirements captured in the project workspace, supported by lot, inspection, and records modules.</li>
  <li><strong>Health and Safety:</strong> Maintain safe workplaces, engage workers via the Consultation Procedure (QSE-5.4-PROC-01), and implement controls through site inspections and the SWMS library.</li>
  <li><strong>Environmental Protection:</strong> Prevent pollution and manage aspects via the Environmental Management Procedure (QSE-8.1-PROC-04) and project EMPs.</li>
  <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Fulfil legal and other obligations catalogued in the Compliance Obligations Register (QSE-6.1-REG-03) with alerts surfaced in the dashboard.</li>
  <li><strong>Risk-Based Thinking:</strong> Identify and treat risks through the corporate risk and opportunity registers (QSE-6.1-REG-01/02) and project-level risk reviews.</li>
  <li><strong>Objectives &amp; Improvement:</strong> Set and monitor objectives recorded in QSE-6.2-PLAN-01, and drive continual improvement actions tracked in QSE-10.3-REG-01.</li>
  <li><strong>Resources &amp; Competence:</strong> Provide competent people, data, and tools using the Training Needs Matrix (QSE-7.2-REG-01) and linked HR integrations.</li>
</ul>
<p>All personnel and partners must comply with this policy. The controlled copy is available to employees via the app navigation and may be shared with interested parties upon request.</p>
<p>This policy is reviewed at least annually during Management Review (QSE-9.3-PROC-01) or when significant changes occur. Updates are versioned in the assets registry and surfaced through the approvals workflow.</p>
<div>
  <p><strong>Approved by:</strong> [CEO Name], Chief Executive Officer</p>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Effective Date]</p>
</div>
'''
